Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我的房子 我的家
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.36,op-eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My house, my home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}很小巧 很漂亮
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.36,op-eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Is so small, so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.36,main-cn,,0,0,0,,有这么多 应该能用上一年吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.36,main-jp,,0,0,0,,これだけあれば１年はもつわね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}妈妈 爸爸
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.36,op-eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My mom, my dad
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:30.48,main-cn,,0,0,0,,但是 月桂树离这里很远的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.77,0:05:30.48,main-jp,,0,0,0,,でも　ローリエのきまでーずいぶん遠いでしょ
